<plot>Raj Malhotra (Amitabh Bachchan) and wife Pooja (Hema Malini) have four sons. The sons have settled down professionally and are quite independent. However, when Raj Malhotra retires, none of his children want to be burdened with the responsibility of taking care of their parents. Strangely, it is the adopted son (played by Salman Khan) who proves to be the most kind hearted of them all. Mahima plays Salman's girlfriend and eventually marries him. The question is, will Raj and Pooja's sons learn the folly of their ways and turn over a new leaf?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?056465</url></doc>
